Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It smells like a rich fruit wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent suddenly turned a little sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's coming from that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body's petrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now just stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. It's just a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can finally breathe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couldn't be. I didn't see any weapons on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that sweet scent disappeared with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was that all about?
