Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.59,0:03:59.55,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an6\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(1264,110)}The Hand that Caresses the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, last night was pretty tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll eat something to get my energy back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have any dried meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, {we }haven't had much luck hunting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy seems to be selling some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him. I'd advise against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His meat always reeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The meat does smell a bit rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any fresh meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tag along and buy some of that instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The meat inside the house smells rotten too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who'd like to buy some of this morning's catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a sweet smell in the midst of the rotten one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the same scent from last night in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. A traveler, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pick out whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you hunting in the mountains last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just butchered these this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been letting them sit out in the sun all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying our meat stinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} don't smell anything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go catch you something fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't have any complaints then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll only be a half hour or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit tight for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder all your meat tastes bad regardless of how fresh it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That hand of yours that helps you hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Any relatives of yours have the same ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our father had it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the palm, there's a mark shaped like an eye, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That mark is proof that you're tainted by fuki, the "Sake of Decay."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki is a decayed form of kouki, which is the essence of all life.{Kouki is also called the "Sake of Light" earlier on in the series.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to become the \Nmushi it was meant to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be found in groundwater and resembles reddish mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells much like fruit wine, but it is toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If ingested in high enough concentrations, it usually causes death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a small number of people are able to tolerate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki itself is not sentient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is merely a "thing" of decay.{it just sits there, "waiting" for more decay}{i guess the original line can stay if it sounds better}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But once it is ingested and enters the bloodstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the fuki {\i1}becomes{\i0} sentient,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and its host gains a special ability:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the ability to give off a sweet smell from their hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which lures in and intoxicates prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuki is then passed down through that host's bloodline for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so {\i1}that's{\i0} what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, only a few can actually gain the ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The descendants who cannot... \Noften do not survive the fuki's toxicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny died coughing up blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My little brother has the same illness she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that's also because of this fuki thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some way to cure it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something, Usuke could{ end up like her}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If the afflicted person drinks enough kouki, \Nthe fuki will dissipate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough with me right now, \Nbut I can get you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great news, isn't it, Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have to put up with that illness much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother isn't the only one who needs treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad... How'd he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you know, that makes this easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should cure yours as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're healthy and strong enough as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll have no problem hunting, even without that ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring back enough for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be longer than a month or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I get back, try not to hunt another human by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... that was {\i1}you{\i0} in the mountains last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always hunt at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Many wild animals are more active at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones around during the day are birds that can't see too well at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Small birds aren't much of a challenge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should at least carry a lantern, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's misleading and reckless not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do, no wild beast will come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I could get around these mountains blindfolded,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and no animal is brave enough to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The moonlight's more than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see yourself as the king of the mountain or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a part of these mountains too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can predict what will or won't kill them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not even the most feared mountain beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the medicine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the old Tatsu back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've changed any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find enough medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Out hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And at such a late hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give Tatsu his medicine right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... Tatsu do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Dad died, Tatsu started to become more like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad would do this a lot too... He was always killing animals we didn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Take that home{,} and butcher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Dad, we've still got plenty at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go sell it or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says our meat stinks too much to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then throw it away, for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu, why's Dad doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad likes the hunt itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever disobey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He may turn around one day and hunt us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever think we're in danger, we'll run away like Mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the ability too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that, Dad started to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird's happening to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's turning invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's shadow is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that same day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, we brought you breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, when a very powerful fuki host passes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,his descendants' abilities become enhanced, as if unleashed from a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In afflicted hosts, fuki spreads until it gains total control over the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the host passes over to the mushi's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But he lost his physical form... as well as his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably still wandering in these mountains somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we don't do something soon, Tatsu's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can smell that sweet scent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi. You made it back, huh, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the kouki for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to drink it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give Usuke his first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink mine when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice, feeling like you rule over the whole mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's time to open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being manipulated by a mushi that doesn't even have conscious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know your place, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give Usuke his, and then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I never want us to feel that way again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we did when {\i1}he{\i0} was alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like we could be hunted down any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I even figured out a way so we can avoid being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the person I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you shoot at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever it was fell down the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move my arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't figure something out soon, the wild beasts will eat me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll be safe here until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The night has never felt this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the darkness has never been... this terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here, Usuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't come out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the birds... attack my arm like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most animals—birds in particular—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,fear marks that resemble eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they were all drawn to that sweet scent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they never attacked your hand, because of that mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But once the "eye" became covered in your fuki-scented blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the birds only saw your arm as irresistible food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Food for the birds, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu, your fever's gone down a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've gotten a lot better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't coughed up any blood at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that kouki thing really worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can learn how to hunt too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get better too so we can go hunting together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.{lol Ginko}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the dark, even the bravest \Nbecome afraid of unseen phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cavorting under the shroud of darkness... are countless misshapen entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if ever there were a king of the creatures of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}surely, it would look just like that.
